data.name: textBox1.Text
data.value:
Instruction!
- Move the snake around to eat food. You'll get one point for each food. -You can check/uncheck wall option to enable/disable the wall
For single Player: -Use arrow Keys to control the snake. -Avoid wall, if wall is enabled, and self body collision.
For Two Player: -For player 1 use arrow Keys to control the snake. -For player 2 use ASWD keys: A to move left, D to move right, W to move up, S to move down. -Avoid colliding to wall, if enabled, self body and another Snake's body.
